<paragraph blockId="89.[151,1436,1590,1725]" pageId="89" pageNumber="90">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,260,1590,1616]" pageId="89" pageNumber="90">Remarks</emphasis>
: Authorship for the family 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Jordan &amp; Gilbert" authorityYear="1879" box="[567,691,1590,1616]" class="Elasmobranchii" family="Dasyatidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Myliobatiformes" pageId="89" pageNumber="90" phylum="Chordata" rank="family">Dasyatidae</taxonomicName>
is often attributed to 
<bibRefCitation author="Jordan" box="[931,1090,1590,1616]" firstAuthor="Jordan" pageId="89" pageNumber="90" refId="ref106053" refString="Jordan, D. S. (1888) A manual of vertebrate animals of the northern United States, including the district north and east of the Ozark mountains, south of the Laurentian hills, north of ... Virginia, and east of the Missouri River; inclusive of marine species. 5 th Edition. A. C. McClurg and company, Chicago, Illinois, 375 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 11640" type="book" year="1888">
<collectingCountry box="[931,1006,1590,1616]" name="Jordan" pageId="89" pageNumber="90">Jordan</collectingCountry>
(1888)
</bibRefCitation>
, but van der Lann 
<emphasis box="[1299,1348,1590,1616]" italics="true" pageId="89" pageNumber="90">et al</emphasis>
. (2014) noted that authorship should be corrected to 
<bibRefCitation author="Jordan &amp; Gilbert" box="[717,1000,1626,1652]" firstAuthor="Jordan" pageId="89" pageNumber="90" pagination="365 - 388" refId="ref106463" refString="Jordan, D. S. &amp; Gilbert, C. H. (1879) Notes on the fishes of Beaufort Harbor, North Carolina. Proceedings of the United States National Museum, 1 (55), 365 - 388. https: // doi. org / 10.5479 / si. 00963801.1 - 55.365" type="journal article" year="1879">
<collectingCountry box="[717,792,1626,1652]" name="Jordan" pageId="89" pageNumber="90">Jordan</collectingCountry>
&amp; Gilbert (1879)
</bibRefCitation>
. In the original description, 
<bibRefCitation author="Jordan &amp; Gilbert" firstAuthor="Jordan" page="386" pageId="89" pageNumber="90" pagination="365 - 388" refId="ref106463" refString="Jordan, D. S. &amp; Gilbert, C. H. (1879) Notes on the fishes of Beaufort Harbor, North Carolina. Proceedings of the United States National Museum, 1 (55), 365 - 388. https: // doi. org / 10.5479 / si. 00963801.1 - 55.365" type="journal article" year="1879">
<collectingCountry box="[1330,1405,1626,1652]" name="Jordan" pageId="89" pageNumber="90">Jordan</collectingCountry>
&amp; Gilbert (1879: 386)
</bibRefCitation>
, the family name was spelled 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Jordan" authorityYear="1888" box="[783,924,1662,1688]" class="Elasmobranchii" family="Dasybatidae" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Myliobatiformes" pageId="89" pageNumber="90" phylum="Chordata" rank="family">Dasybatidae</taxonomicName>
, but later corrected by 
<bibRefCitation author="Jordan" box="[1198,1404,1662,1688]" firstAuthor="Jordan" page="22" pageId="89" pageNumber="90" refId="ref106053" refString="Jordan, D. S. (1888) A manual of vertebrate animals of the northern United States, including the district north and east of the Ozark mountains, south of the Laurentian hills, north of ... Virginia, and east of the Missouri River; inclusive of marine species. 5 th Edition. A. C. McClurg and company, Chicago, Illinois, 375 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 11640" type="book" year="1888">
<collectingCountry box="[1198,1273,1662,1688]" name="Jordan" pageId="89" pageNumber="90">Jordan</collectingCountry>
(1888: 22)
</bibRefCitation>
to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Jordan &amp; Gilbert" authorityYear="1879" box="[198,322,1698,1724]" class="Elasmobranchii" family="Dasyatidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Myliobatiformes" pageId="89" pageNumber="90" phylum="Chordata" rank="family">Dasyatidae</taxonomicName>
(van der Lann 
<emphasis box="[493,543,1698,1724]" italics="true" pageId="89" pageNumber="90">et al</emphasis>
., 2014; 
<bibRefCitation author="Last" box="[634,834,1698,1725]" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="Last" pageId="89" pageNumber="90" pagination="345 - 368" refId="ref107497" refString="Last, P. R., Naylor, G. J. P. &amp; Manjaji-Matsumoto, B. M. (2016 h) A revised classification of the family Dasyatidae (Chondrichthyes: Myliobatiformes) based on new morphological and molecular insights. Zootaxa, 4139 (3), 345 - 368. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4139.3.2" type="journal article" year="2016" yearSuffix="h">
Last 
<emphasis box="[689,739,1698,1724]" italics="true" pageId="89" pageNumber="90">et al</emphasis>
., 2016h
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
